Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.52,0:04:44.80,辉英,,0,0,0,,I highly recommend this documentary on the Voyager space probes,
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.90,辉中,,0,0,0,,介绍了它漫游太阳系的旅程
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.90,辉英,,0,0,0,,which looks at their wild ride through the solar system
